data.description: Situated within the Lakefront community of Seven Coves, this exceptional 4-5 bedroom home offers access to boat launches, fishing areas, parks, tennis courts, pool + great schools. It possesses immense potential to become a dream home w/a few modifications to cater to the preferences of the next owner. The exterior features an over-sized garage, large fenced backyard, both upper and lower covered patios, providing ample space to install a private pool. The interior radiates a welcoming vibe, adorned with high ceilings embellished with accent beams and a wall of windows. The open floor plan, seamlessly connecting the island kitchen to the spacious living room centered around a fireplace. Located on the first floor, the primary bedroom features a stunning vaulted ceiling, double sinks, a spacious walk-in shower, and an expansive closet. Upstairs, three expansive bedrooms await, attached Jack/Jill bathroom& an additional full bathroom, game room w/a private outdoor balcony & a media room.
